org.hibernate.type.StandardBasicTypes.StandardBasicType

  • Packages that use StandardBasicTypes.StandardBasicType 
    Package Description
    org.hibernate.type
    A Hibernate Type is a strategy for mapping a Java property type to a JDBC type or types.
